  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Over 18 years last seen normal between 8 - 24 hours, without prior history of
             intravenous plasminogen activator (IV t-PA ) or

          -  mechanical thrombectomy Vessels - intracranial vertebral artery, basilar artery,
             intracranial ICA, ICA terminus bifurcation, MCA M1/M2, or

          -  ACA NIHSS ≥ 7 MRI DWI/PWI or

          -  CTA/P, which demonstrates an area of mismatch ≥ 2/3 rd

          -  Signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  creat &gt;= 2

          -  NIHSS &lt; 7

          -  Baseline mRS &gt;= 2

          -  infarct &gt; 1/3rd MCA territory

          -  competing trials

          -  prior IV or IA treatment
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
